      %li A binary data interchange mechanism (File API)
      %li Useful for moving data around
      %li 
        Basic API for:
        %ul 
          %li
            %strong size
            \: size in bytes of the blob
          %li
            %strong type
            \: MIME type of the data contained in the blob
          %li
            %strong slice(start, end, contentType)
